{"tid":1986202,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得615發生咩事","createTime":"2020-04-23T16:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T01:59:38.000Z","uid":40743,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"80d36d59ba46c64c6c147bb0b248fdb28c6f69c0","tid":1986202,"uid":40743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:28:53.000Z","msg":"過咗咁多個月了，發生嘅事一路累積<br />\n<br />\n希望手足門唔好忘記初心，唔好比港共老招數玩弄！<br />\n<br />\n矛頭對翻港共，面向翻我地嘅敵人！<br />\n<br />\n團結係我地唯一僅有嘅武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發生太多傷心痛苦事，大家記憶都開始自我保護<br />\n每日都要問自己，是真的忘記，還是害怕記起？"},{"pid":"0417e0382b8b0da38cab5fa7ccba8fd88d11b407","tid":1986202,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"本班為615綫列車前往屯門碼頭"},{"pid":"9d87da5d241daa9f0b56c3a0ea30ef3e65863054","tid":1986202,"uid":704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0417e0382b8b0da38cab5fa7ccba8fd88d11b407","tid":1986202,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"本班為615綫列車前往屯門碼頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"This is route 615 to ferry pier"},{"pid":"7ea46d62300fb8bbf3b7928f8eb149444351e929","tid":1986202,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />